cu.explanation_en: Setting the NG-AMF IP to an unreachable address will cause SCTP connection failure and prevent control plane setup.

du.explanation_en: Setting the uplink carrier offset to an out-of-range value will cause frequency misalignment and prevent proper uplink carrier allocation and UE transmission.
du.explanation_zh: 將上行載波偏移設定為超出範圍的值會導致頻率錯位，並阻止正確的上行載波分配和 UE 傳輸。
